responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "95B0999B4C988B37CB22BEB2AE7A5CFC", "My lumberjacks have been frightened off and eaten by a massive beast of a bear. This monster is our namesake, Timberclaw! Twice the size of a normal bear and immortal. At least that\'s what Bearskin says.")
